title: Ep. 131 - Get Ready for $200 Oil
itunes:title: Get Ready for $200 Oil
description: Dr. Kent Moors, one of the world's most well respected energy analysts, predicts oil prices will rise significantly over the next few years. Dr. Moors also shares five reasons why natural gas prices are about to rally.
